 472:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_ll_fmc.c ****                     ##### How to use NAND device driver #####
 473:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_ll_fmc.c ****   ==============================================================================
 474:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_ll_fmc.c ****   [..]
 475:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_ll_fmc.c ****     This driver contains a set of APIs to interface with the FMC NAND banks in order
 476:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_ll_fmc.c ****     to run the NAND external devices.
 477:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_ll_fmc.c **** 
 478:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_ll_fmc.c ****     (+) FMC NAND bank reset using the function FMC_NAND_DeInit()
 479:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_ll_fmc.c ****     (+) FMC NAND bank control configuration using the function FMC_NAND_Init()
 480:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_ll_fmc.c ****     (+) FMC NAND bank common space timing configuration using the function
 481:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_ll_fmc.c ****         FMC_NAND_CommonSpace_Timing_Init()
